## Empty States

### EmptyState Component

**Component:** `EmptyState` (in `shared.tsx`)  
**Scope:** No data returned; user action needed (upload first report, no alerts, etc.)  
**Trigger:** Data fetch returns empty array, user hasn't taken action yet

#### Layout — Default Variant

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                               │
│                  📭 (large icon)              │
│          No reports yet                      │
│  Upload your first medical report            │
│                                               │
│  [ Upload Report ]                          │
│                                               │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

#### Layout — Compact Variant

```
┌──────────────────────┐
│  📭 No alerts       │
│  [ View All → ]     │
└──────────────────────┘
```

#### Props

```typescript
interface EmptyStateProps {
  message: string;                   // Main message
  icon?: React.ReactNode;            // Emoji or icon element
  action?: {                         // Optional CTA
    label: string;
    onClick: () => void;
  };
  subtext?: string;                  // Additional explanation
  variant?: "default" | "compact";   // Layout size (default: "default")
}
```

#### Common Empty State Scenarios

| Page / Section | Message | Icon | Action | Subtext |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Reports** | No reports yet | 📄 | Upload Report | Upload your first medical report to get started |
| **Alerts** | No active alerts | ✅ | Browse Archived | You're all caught up! |
| **Chat History** | No messages | 💬 | Start Chat | Ask the AI assistant anything |
| **Doctors List** | No doctors assigned | 👨‍⚕️ | Request Access | No doctors have been assigned yet |
| **Search Results** | No matches found | 🔍 | Clear Filters | Try different search terms |
| **Trends** | Not enough data | 📊 | Sync Wearable | Sync wearable for 7+ days |

#### Usage

```tsx
import { EmptyState } from "@/components/ui/shared";

function AlertsList({ alerts }) {
  if (alerts.length === 0) {
    return (
      <EmptyState
        icon="✅"
        message="No active alerts"
        subtext="You're all caught up! Check your archived alerts."
        action={{
          label: "View Archived",
          onClick: () => navigate("/alerts?filter=archived")
        }}
        variant="default"
      />
    );
  }

  return <div>{/* Alerts content */}</div>;
}
```

#### QA Test Cases

- ✅ **Default variant:** Verify centered, large layout
- ✅ **Compact variant:** Verify smaller, inline layout
- ✅ **Icon rendering:** Emoji displays correctly
- ✅ **Action button:** Click triggers callback
- ✅ **Without action:** No button renders if action not provided
- ✅ **Subtext display:** Secondary text shows when provided
- ✅ **Responsive:** Layout adapts to mobile/desktop

